select 
	gs.SHIFTDATE 		as SHIFTDATE,
	o.MIDSERVER,
	o.ICOMMONSHIFT 		as 'SHIFTNUM',
    PE.AUTHCODE 		as AUTHCODE,
	r.name 				as 'Restaurant',
	r.CODE 				as RESTCODE,
	MI.Code 			as 'Dish_Code',
	MI.NAME 			as 'Dish_Name',
	cast(sum(sd.quantity) as bigint) 	as 'QNT',
	cast(sum(SD.SRCQUANTITY) as bigint) as 'Source_QNT',
	sd.STATE 			as STATE_DISH,
	sd.SIFR 			as SIFR_MENUITEMS,
	o.VISIT, 
	o.IDENTINVISIT 		AS ORDERIDENT,
	o.MAINWAITER,
	o.STATIONID,
	o.ORDERNAME,
	o.IAUTHOR,
	TP.TAXRATE,
	TP.SUM 				as SUM_TAXPARTS,
	cast(DV.QUANTITY as bigint) 		as DISHVOIDQUANTITY,
	DV.PRLISTSUM 		as DISHVOIDPRLISTSUM,
	PB.UNI 				as UNI_PAYBINDINGSUNI,
	PB.PRICESUM, 
	PB.PAYSUM,
	PB.DISTRDISCOUNTS,
	PB.QUANTITY,
	CL.SIFR 			as SIFR_CURRLINES,
	CL.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
	SD2.SIFR 			as COMBODISHUNI_SIFRMENUITEMS,
	SD2.STATE 			as STATE_COMBO,
	SD2.UNI 			as COMBOUNI,
	cast(SD2.QUANTITY as int) 		as COMBOQUANTITY,
	PE.OWNER 			as CARDTYPE,		
	PE.CARDNUM 			as CARDNUM,
	PE.ACCOUNTIDENT,
	PE.TRANSACTIONID,
	PE.EXTTRANSACTIONINFO,
	gs.CLOSETIME,												
	gs.STARTTIME,
Getdate() as gp_load_date
from [RK_Central].dbo.GLOBALSHIFTS (NOLOCK) as gs 
	join [RK_Central].dbo.RESTAURANTS (NOLOCK) as r  on r.sifr=gs.IRESTAURANT
	join [RK_Central].dbo.ORDERS (NOLOCK) as o on o.MIDSERVER=gs.MIDSERVER and O.ICOMMONSHIFT=GS.SHIFTNUM
	join [RK_Central].dbo.SESSIONDISHES (NOLOCK) as SD on SD.MIDSERVER=O.MIDSERVER and SD.VISIT=O.VISIT and SD.ORDERIDENT=o.IDENTINVISIT
	join [RK_Central].dbo.MENUITEMS (NOLOCK) as mi on mi.sifr=sd.SIFR
	LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PAYBINDINGS (NOLOCK) as PB ON O.MIDSERVER = PB.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PB.VISIT AND PB.DISHUNI = SD.UNI
	LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.TAXPARTS (NOLOCK) as TP ON O.MIDSERVER = TP.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = TP.VISIT AND PB.UNI = TP.BINDINGUNI
	left Join [RK_Central].dbo.PRINTCHECKS (NOLOCK) as PC on PC.MIDSERVER=O.MIDSERVER and PC.VISIT=O.VISIT
	LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.SESSIONDISHES (NOLOCK) as SD2 ON O.MIDSERVER = SD2.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = SD2.VISIT AND O.IDENTINVISIT = SD2.ORDERIDENT AND SD.COMBODISHUNI = SD2.UNI
	LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.CURRLINES (NOLOCK) as CL ON O.MIDSERVER = CL.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = CL.VISIT AND PC.UNI = CL.CHECKUNI AND CL.UNI = PB.CURRUNI
	LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PAYMENTSEXTRA (NOLOCK) as PE ON O.MIDSERVER = PE.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PE.VISIT AND CL.PAYUNIFOROWNERINFO = PE.PAYUNI
	left Join 
        (SELECT
             MIDSERVER,
             VISIT,
             DISHUNI,
             SUM(PRLISTSUM) 	as PRLISTSUM,
             SUM(QUANTITY) 	as QUANTITY
        FROM
            [RK_Central].dbo.DISHVOIDS (NOLOCK)
        GROUP BY
             MIDSERVER,
             VISIT,
             DISHUNI) as DV on DV.MIDSERVER=o.MIDSERVER AND DV.VISIT=o.VISIT AND DV.DISHUNI=sd.UNI
	where 
		pc.VISIT is null
and gs.SHIFTDATE >= dateadd(day,-4, getdate()) and gs.SHIFTDATE <= getdate()
group by
	r.name,
	r.CODE,
	MI.Code,
	MI.NAME,
	sd.SIFR ,
	o.MIDSERVER,
	o.VISIT,
	o.ICOMMONSHIFT,
	o.IDENTINVISIT,
	o.MAINWAITER,
	o.STATIONID,
	o.ORDERNAME,
	o.IAUTHOR,
	TP.TAXRATE,
	TP.SUM,
	DV.QUANTITY ,			
	DV.PRLISTSUM,
    PE.OWNER,		
    PE.CARDNUM,
	PE.AUTHCODE,
	PE.ACCOUNTIDENT,
    PE.TRANSACTIONID,
	PE.EXTTRANSACTIONINFO,
    gs.CLOSETIME,												
    gs.STARTTIME,
    SD2.SIFR,
    SD2.STATE,
    SD2.UNI ,
    SD2.QUANTITY ,
	CL.SIFR,
	CL.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
	sd.STATE,
	PB.UNI,
	PB.PRICESUM, 
	PB.PAYSUM,
	PB.DISTRDISCOUNTS,
	PB.QUANTITY,
	gs.SHIFTDATE

properties.SQL select query:
delete from rkeeper.dt1_nonfiscal
where shiftdate >= now()::date - 4 *interval'1 day'

SELECT DISTINCT
        GS.SHIFTDATE,
        O.MIDSERVER,
        O.VISIT,
        O.ICOMMONSHIFT as SHIFTNUM,
        (case when isnull(pa.PRINTER,0) > 1  then C.SIFR end) NONFISCSTATION,
        (case when isnull(pa.PRINTER,0) > 1  then CG.SIFR end) NONFISCSERVER, getdate() as gp_load_date
    FROM 
        [RK_Central].dbo.GLOBALSHIFTS (NOLOCK) GS
        JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.ORDERS (NOLOCK) O ON O.MIDSERVER = GS.MIDSERVER AND O.ICOMMONSHIFT = GS.SHIFTNUM
        JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.VISITS (NOLOCK) V ON V.MIDSERVER = O.MIDSERVER AND V.SIFR = O.VISIT
        JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.ORDERSESSIONS (NOLOCK) OS ON OS.MIDSERVER = O.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = OS.VISIT AND O.IDENTINVISIT = OS.ORDERIDENT
        JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PRINTCHECKS (NOLOCK) PC ON PC.MIDSERVER = OS.MIDSERVER AND PC.VISIT = OS.VISIT AND PC.SESSIONUNI = OS.UNI AND PC.STATE = 6
        JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.CASHES (NOLOCK) C on C.STTYPE = 1 and C.Colors = 0 and C.CASHGROUP = OS.MIDSERVER and C.SIFR = OS.ISTATION
        JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.CASHGROUPS (NOLOCK) CG on CG.SIFR = C.CASHGROUP
        JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.RESTAURANTS (NOLOCK) R ON r.SIFR = GS.IRESTAURANT
        JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PRINTERASSIGNS (NOLOCK) PA on pa.OBJID = C.sifr and pa.PURPOSE = 3
    WHERE 
                GS.SHIFTDATE >= dateadd(day,-4, convert(date, getdate()))
and
                GS.SHIFTDATE < convert(date, getdate())

SELECT 	
                     R.CODE 				as RESTCODE,		
                     O.MIDSERVER, 												
                     O.VISIT, 													
                     O.ICOMMONSHIFT 		as SHIFTNUM,				
                     O.COT 				    as OUTTYPE,			
                     O.UOT 				    as ORDERCATEGORY,	
                     O.OPENTIME 			as OPENTIME,
                     GS.SHIFTDATE, 	
                     GS.IRESTAURANT 		as RESTSIFR,											
                     GS.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,										
                     GS.CLOSETIME,												
                     GS.STARTTIME,	
                     PC.GUIDSTRING,
                     PC.CHECKNUM,												
                     PC.GLOBALIDENT,	
                     PC.STARTDATETIME,											
                     PC.CLOSEDATETIME,
                     PC.STATE,											
                     PC.IPRINTSTATION,
                     PC.ICLOSESTATION,
                     PC.ICREATOR,
                     PC.IAUTHOR,
                     PC.IFISCSHIFT,
                     PC.EXTFISCID,
                     PC.PRINTNUMBER,
                     PC.FISCDOCNUMBER,
                     PC.DELETEFISCDOCNUMBER,
                     PC.BINDEDSUM,
                     CL.SIFR 			    as SIFR_CURRLINES,
                     CL.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
                     PB.UNI 				as UNI_PAYBINDINGSUNI,
                     PB.PRICESUM, 
                     PB.PAYSUM,
                     PB.DISTRDISCOUNTS,
                     PB.QUANTITY,
                     TP.TAXRATE,
                     TP.SUM 				as SUM_TAXPARTS,
                     SD1.SIFR 			    as SIFR_MENUITEMS,
                     SD1.STATE 			    as STATE_DISH,
                     SD1.UNI 			    as DISHUNI,
             	     SD1.SESSIONUNI			as DISH_SESSIONUNI,
             	     SD1.SORTORDER			as DISH_SORTORDER,
                     SD2.SIFR 			    as COMBODISHUNI_SIFRMENUITEMS,
                     SD2.STATE 			    as STATE_COMBO,
                     SD2.UNI 			    as COMBOUNI,
                     SD2.QUANTITY 			as COMBOQUANTITY,
                     PE.OWNER 			    as CARDTYPE,		
                     PE.CARDNUM 			as CARDNUM,
             	     PE.AUTHCODE 			as AUTHCODE,
             	     PE.ACCOUNTIDENT,
                     PE.TRANSACTIONID,
             	     PE.EXTTRANSACTIONINFO,
                     DV.QUANTITY 			as DISHVOIDQUANTITY,
                     DV.PRLISTSUM 			as DISHVOIDPRLISTSUM,
                     PC.DELETEDATETIME 		AS DELETEDATETIME,
                     O.GUIDSTRING 			as GUID_ORDERS,
                     Getdate() as gp_load_date
                 FROM 
                     [RK_Central].dbo.ORDERS (NOLOCK) as O
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.GLOBALSHIFTS (NOLOCK) as GS ON O.MIDSERVER = GS.MIDSERVER AND O.ICOMMONSHIFT = GS.SHIFTNUM
                     JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PRINTCHECKS (NOLOCK) as PC ON O.MIDSERVER = PC.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PC.VISIT AND O.IDENTINVISIT = PC.ORDERIDENT
                     JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.SESSIONDISHES (NOLOCK) as SD1 ON O.MIDSERVER = SD1.MIDSERVER AND O.IDENTINVISIT = SD1.ORDERIDENT AND O.VISIT = SD1.VISIT AND SD1.ISCOMBO = 0
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PAYBINDINGS (NOLOCK) as PB ON O.MIDSERVER = PB.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PB.VISIT AND PB.DISHUNI = SD1.UNI AND PB.STATE = '6'      
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.CURRLINES (NOLOCK) as CL ON O.MIDSERVER = CL.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = CL.VISIT AND PC.UNI = CL.CHECKUNI AND CL.UNI = PB.CURRUNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.TAXPARTS (NOLOCK) as TP ON O.MIDSERVER = TP.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = TP.VISIT AND PB.UNI = TP.BINDINGUNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.SESSIONDISHES (NOLOCK) as SD2 ON O.MIDSERVER = SD2.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = SD2.VISIT AND O.IDENTINVISIT = SD2.ORDERIDENT AND SD1.COMBODISHUNI = SD2.UNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PAYMENTSEXTRA (NOLOCK) as PE ON O.MIDSERVER = PE.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PE.VISIT AND CL.PAYUNIFOROWNERINFO = PE.PAYUNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.RESTAURANTS (NOLOCK) as R ON GS.IRESTAURANT = R.SIFR
                     LEFT JOIN 
                     (SELECT
                          MIDSERVER,
                          VISIT,
                          DISHUNI,
                          SUM(PRLISTSUM) 	as PRLISTSUM,
                          SUM(QUANTITY) 	as QUANTITY
                     FROM
                          [RK_Central].dbo.DISHVOIDS (NOLOCK)
                     GROUP BY
                          MIDSERVER,
                          VISIT,
                          DISHUNI) as DV ON O.MIDSERVER = DV.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = DV.VISIT AND SD1.UNI = DV.DISHUNI
                     --LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.ZREPORTDATA (NOLOCK) as ZR ON O.MIDSERVER = ZR.MIDSERVER AND O.ICOMMONSHIFT = ZR.SHIFTNUM
                 WHERE
                    gs.shiftdate = cast('${shiftdate}' as datetime)

Рекомендуется раз в две недели/месяц проверять работоспособность

Изначально данные будут разделены на части, 
чтобы их было легче прогружать. После уже данные
отправляются на процессор загрузки в Greenplum.

В случае ошибки ( внутренняя ошибка NIFI, 
зависли данные, долгое ожидание и пр) данные еще 
несколько раз будут пробовать попасть внутрь БД 
( после нескольких попыток упадут в лог ошибок, 
если не смогли загрузиться).

Если произошла неудача при вставке данных или их обработке, 
то делается несколько попыток еще раз реализовать процесс...

запись в лог и отправке уведомления об ошибке.

        JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.ORDERS (NOLOCK) O ON (O.VISIT = PC.VISIT) AND (O.MIDSERVER = PC.MIDSERVER) AND (O.IDENTINVISIT = PC.ORDERIDENT)

        JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.GLOBALSHIFTS (NOLOCK) GS ON (GS.MIDSERVER = O.MIDSERVER) AND (GS.SHIFTNUM = O.ICOMMONSHIFT)
        LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.RESTAURANTS (NOLOCK) R ON GS.IRESTAURANT=R.SIFR
        LEFT JOIN ( 
            SELECT 
                VISIT, 
                MIDSERVER, 
                ORDERIDENT,
                MAX(CASE WHEN ISESSIONTYPE=5 THEN 5 ELSE 0 END) AS "ISESSIONTYPE" 
            FROM 
                [RK_Central].dbo.ORDERSESSIONS (NOLOCK)
            GROUP BY
                VISIT, 
                MIDSERVER, 
                ORDERIDENT) OS
        ON (OS.MIDSERVER=O.MIDSERVER) AND (OS.VISIT=O.VISIT) AND (OS.ORDERIDENT=O.IDENTINVISIT)
    WHERE 
        OS.ISESSIONTYPE=5
        AND 
        (PC.IGNOREINREP=0)
        AND 
        (GS.STATUS=3) 
        AND 
        (EI.VISIT IS NULL OR EI.EXTSOURCE <> '120')
        AND 
        (GPD.SIFR IS NULL OR GPD.PROPERTYVAL <> '3')

SELECT  DiscParts.SIFR as DiscType,
  			sum(DiscParts."SUM") AS "DISCSUM",                                                                                                                    
  			Discounts00."NAME" AS "DISCOUNT",                                                                                                  
  			DishDiscounts00."HOLDER" AS "HOLDER",                                                                                                                
  			PrintChecks00."CHECKNUM" AS "CHECKNUM",                                                                                                              
  			DishDiscounts00."CARDCODE" AS "CARDCODE",                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
  			GlobalShifts00."SHIFTNUM" AS "SHIFTNUM",                                                                                                             
  			GlobalShifts00."SHIFTDATE" AS "SHIFTDATE",                                                                                                           
  			CashGroups00."NETNAME" AS "NETNAME",
  			CURRENCIES00."NAME" AS "CURRENCY",
  			ORIGCURRENCIES."NAME" AS "ORIGCURRENCY",
  			Restaurants00."NAME" AS "RESTAURANTNAME",
            Restaurants00.CODE AS REST_CODE,
  			(CASE WHEN (ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY Discounts00."NAME",                                   
     			  DishDiscounts00."CARDCODE",                                                                              
     			  GlobalShifts00."SHIFTNUM",                                                                                                             
     			  GlobalShifts00."SHIFTDATE",                                                                                                           
     			  CashGroups00."NETNAME",
     			  Restaurants00."NAME" ORDER BY DishDiscounts00."CARDCODE")=1) THEN 1 
     			           ELSE 0
     			           END) AS "DISCOUNTVISIT", getdate() as gp_load_date
	FROM [RK_Central].dbo.DISCPARTS                                                                                                                                         
		LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PAYBINDINGS    PayBindings00                                                                                                                    
		  ON (PayBindings00.Visit = DiscParts.Visit) AND (PayBindings00.MidServer = DiscParts.MidServer) AND (PayBindings00.UNI = DiscParts.BindingUNI)     
		LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.CurrLines CurrLines00                                                                                                                        
		  ON (CurrLines00.Visit = PayBindings00.Visit) AND (CurrLines00.MidServer = PayBindings00.MidServer) AND (CurrLines00.UNI = PayBindings00.CurrUNI)     
		LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PAYMENTS  PAYMENTS01
		  ON (PAYMENTS01.Visit = CurrLines00.Visit) AND (PAYMENTS01.MidServer = CurrLines00.MidServer) AND (PAYMENTS01.UNI = CurrLines00.PayUNIForOwnerInfo )
		LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PrintChecks  PrintChecks00                                                                                                                    
		  ON (PrintChecks00.Visit = CurrLines00.Visit) AND (PrintChecks00.MidServer = CurrLines00.MidServer) AND (PrintChecks00.UNI = CurrLines00.CheckUNI)    
		LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.trk7EnumsValues  trk7EnumsValues0800                                                                                                          
		  ON (trk7EnumsValues0800.EnumData = PrintChecks00.State) AND (trk7EnumsValues0800.EnumName = 'TDrawItemState')                                        
		LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.DishDiscounts  DishDiscounts00                                                                                                                
		  ON (DishDiscounts00.Visit = DiscParts.Visit) AND (DishDiscounts00.MidServer = DiscParts.MidServer) AND (DishDiscounts00.UNI = DiscParts.DiscLineUNI) 
		LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.Discounts  Discounts00
		  ON (Discounts00.SIFR = DishDiscounts00.Sifr)
		LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.Orders  Orders00                                                                                                                              
		  ON (Orders00.Visit = PrintChecks00.Visit) AND (Orders00.MidServer = PrintChecks00.MidServer) AND (Orders00.IdentInVisit = PrintChecks00.OrderIdent)  
		LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.GlobalShifts  GlobalShifts00                                                                                                                  
		  ON (GlobalShifts00.MidServer = Orders00.MidServer) AND (GlobalShifts00.ShiftNum = Orders00.iCommonShift)                                             
		LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.CashGroups  CashGroups00                                                                                                                      
		  ON (CashGroups00.SIFR = PrintChecks00.Midserver)                                                                                                     
		LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.Restaurants  Restaurants00
		  ON (Restaurants00.SIFR = CashGroups00.Restaurant)
		LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PaymentsExtra  PaymentsExtra00
		  ON (PaymentsExtra00.Visit = CurrLines00.Visit) AND (PaymentsExtra00.MidServer = CurrLines00.MidServer) AND (PaymentsExtra00.PayUNI = CurrLines00.PayUNIForOwnerInfo)
		LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PDSCards  PDSCards00
		  ON (PDSCards00.AccountIdent = PaymentsExtra00.AccountIdent) AND (PDSCards00.MInterface = PaymentsExtra00.AddByInterface)
		LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PDSCards  PDSCards01
		  ON (PDSCards01.AccountIdent = DishDiscounts00.AccountIdent) AND (PDSCards01.MInterface = DishDiscounts00.MINTERFACE)
		     AND PDSCards01.CARDCODE=DishDiscounts00.CARDCODE
		LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.CURRENCIES CURRENCIES00
		  ON  CURRENCIES00.SIFR=CurrLines00.SIFR 
		LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.CURRENCIES ORIGCURRENCIES 
		  ON  ORIGCURRENCIES.SIFR=PAYMENTS01.SIFR 
		WHERE                                                                                                                                                  
		  PrintChecks00.State = 6    and 
		  GlobalShifts00."SHIFTDATE" >= dateadd(day,-4, convert(date, getdate())) and GlobalShifts00."SHIFTDATE" <= convert(date, getdate())
		  and DiscParts.SIFR='1015669' and DiscParts."SUM"!=0
		group by DiscParts.SIFR,
		  DishDiscounts00."HOLDER", 
		  PrintChecks00."CHECKNUM" ,
		  DishDiscounts00."CARDCODE",
		  GlobalShifts00."SHIFTNUM",
		  GlobalShifts00."SHIFTDATE",
		  CashGroups00."NETNAME",
		  Restaurants00."NAME",
          Restaurants00.CODE,
		  Discounts00."NAME",
		  CURRENCIES00.NAME,
		  ORIGCURRENCIES.NAME;

SELECT
        t.RESTCODE,
        t.MIDSERVER,
        t.SHIFTNUM,
        t.SHIFTDATE,
        t.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
        0 as SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
        t.STATE,
        Sum(t.BINDEDSUM) as [DB_BINDEDSUM],
        Sum(COUNT) as [DB_COUNT]
    FROM
        (
        SELECT
        	tmp.RESTCODE,
	        tmp.MIDSERVER,
	        tmp.VISIT,
	        tmp.SHIFTNUM,
	        tmp.SHIFTDATE,
	        tmp.STATE,
	        ISNULL(tmp.IHIGHLEVELTYPE, 0) as IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
	        tmp.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,       
	        Round(max(tmp.BINDEDSUM), 0) as BINDEDSUM,
	        Count(tmp.BINDEDSUM)  as COUNT
	    FROM
	        (
	        SELECT
		        O.MIDSERVER, 												
		        O.VISIT, 													
		        O.ICOMMONSHIFT as SHIFTNUM,				
		        GS.SHIFTDATE, 	
		        GS.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,										
		        PC.STATE,											
		        PC.BINDEDSUM,
		        CL.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
		        R.CODE as RESTCODE
		    FROM 
		        [RK_Central].dbo.ORDERS (NOLOCK) as O
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.GLOBALSHIFTS (NOLOCK) as GS ON O.MIDSERVER = GS.MIDSERVER AND O.ICOMMONSHIFT = GS.SHIFTNUM
                     JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PRINTCHECKS (NOLOCK) as PC ON O.MIDSERVER = PC.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PC.VISIT AND O.IDENTINVISIT = PC.ORDERIDENT
                     JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.SESSIONDISHES (NOLOCK) as SD1 ON O.MIDSERVER = SD1.MIDSERVER AND O.IDENTINVISIT = SD1.ORDERIDENT AND O.VISIT = SD1.VISIT AND SD1.ISCOMBO = 0
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PAYBINDINGS (NOLOCK) as PB ON O.MIDSERVER = PB.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PB.VISIT AND PB.DISHUNI = SD1.UNI AND PB.STATE = '6'      
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.CURRLINES (NOLOCK) as CL ON O.MIDSERVER = CL.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = CL.VISIT AND PC.UNI = CL.CHECKUNI AND CL.UNI = PB.CURRUNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.TAXPARTS (NOLOCK) as TP ON O.MIDSERVER = TP.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = TP.VISIT AND PB.UNI = TP.BINDINGUNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.SESSIONDISHES (NOLOCK) as SD2 ON O.MIDSERVER = SD2.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = SD2.VISIT AND O.IDENTINVISIT = SD2.ORDERIDENT AND SD1.COMBODISHUNI = SD2.UNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PAYMENTSEXTRA (NOLOCK) as PE ON O.MIDSERVER = PE.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PE.VISIT AND CL.PAYUNIFOROWNERINFO = PE.PAYUNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.RESTAURANTS (NOLOCK) as R ON GS.IRESTAURANT = R.SIFR
                     LEFT JOIN 
                     (SELECT
                          MIDSERVER,
                          VISIT,
                          DISHUNI,
                          SUM(PRLISTSUM) 	as PRLISTSUM,
                          SUM(QUANTITY) 	as QUANTITY
                     FROM
                          [RK_Central].dbo.DISHVOIDS (NOLOCK)
                     GROUP BY
                          MIDSERVER,
                          VISIT,
                          DISHUNI) as DV ON O.MIDSERVER = DV.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = DV.VISIT AND SD1.UNI = DV.DISHUNI
		    WHERE 
		                  gs.shiftdate >= DATEADD(day, -14 , GETDATE()) and gs.shiftdate <= DATEADD(day, -6 , GETDATE())
		    )tmp 
	    Group By 
	        tmp.RESTCODE,
	        tmp.MIDSERVER,
	        tmp.VISIT,
	        tmp.SHIFTNUM,
	        tmp.SHIFTDATE,
	        ISNULL(tmp.IHIGHLEVELTYPE, 0),
            tmp.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
	        tmp.STATE
		) t
    Group By 
        t.RESTCODE,
         t.MIDSERVER,
         t.SHIFTNUM,
         t.SHIFTDATE,
         t.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
         t.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
         t.STATE

insert into rkeeper.fact_db_dt1 (RESTCODE, MIDSERVER, SHIFTNUM, SHIFTDATE, IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
        SHIFTLOADDATETIME,  STATE , DB_BINDEDSUM,   DB_COUNT)
select 
        t.RESTCODE,
        t.MIDSERVER,
        t.SHIFTNUM,
        t.SHIFTDATE,
        t.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
        0 as SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
        t.STATE,
        Sum(t.BINDEDSUM) as DB_BINDEDSUM,
        Sum(COUNT) as DB_COUNT
    FROM
        (
        SELECT
        	tmp.RESTCODE,
	        tmp.MIDSERVER,
	        tmp.VISIT,
	        tmp.SHIFTNUM,
	        tmp.SHIFTDATE,
	        tmp.STATE,
	        case when tmp.IHIGHLEVELTYPE is null then 0 else tmp.IHIGHLEVELTYPE end as IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
	        tmp.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,       
	        Round(max(tmp.BINDEDSUM), 0) as BINDEDSUM,
	        Count(tmp.BINDEDSUM)  as COUNT
	    FROM
	        (
	        SELECT
		        df.MIDSERVER, 												
		        df.VISIT, 													
		        df.SHIFTNUM,				
		        df.SHIFTDATE, 	
		        df.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,										
		        df.STATE,											
		        df.BINDEDSUM,
		        df.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
		        df.RESTCODE
		    FROM 
		        rkeeper.dt1_fact df
		    WHERE 
		        df.shiftdate >= now() - 14*interval '1 day' and df.shiftdate <= now() - 6*interval '1 day' 
		    )tmp
	    Group By 
	        tmp.RESTCODE,
	        tmp.MIDSERVER,
	        tmp.VISIT,
	        tmp.SHIFTNUM,
	        tmp.SHIFTDATE,
	        tmp.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
	        tmp.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
	        tmp.STATE
		) t
    Group By 
        t.RESTCODE,
         t.MIDSERVER,
         t.SHIFTNUM,
         t.SHIFTDATE,
         t.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
         t.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
         t.STATE

        fs2.STATE as source_STATE,
        fdd.DB_BINDEDSUM as dt1_DB_BINDEDSUM,
        fdd.DB_COUNT as dt1_DB_COUNT,
        fs2.DB_BINDEDSUM as source_DB_BINDEDSUM,
        fs2.DB_COUNT as source_DB_COUNT

full outer join rkeeper.fact_db_dt1 fdd on

        fdd.MIDSERVER = fs2.MIDSERVER
        and fdd.SHIFTNUM = fs2.SHIFTNUM
        and fdd.SHIFTDATE = fs2.SHIFTDATE
        and fdd.IHIGHLEVELTYPE = fs2.IHIGHLEVELTYPE
        and fdd.SHIFTLOADDATETIME = fs2.SHIFTLOADDATETIME
        and fdd.STATE = fs2.STATE 
where (fdd.DB_BINDEDSUM <> fs2.DB_BINDEDSUM or fdd.DB_COUNT <> fs2.DB_COUNT)  
or (fs2.SHIFTNUM is null)

select MIDSERVER, SHIFTNUM, SHIFTDATE
 	from rkeeper.dt1_wrk_newshifts_4;

SELECT
        t.RESTCODE,
        t.MIDSERVER,
        t.SHIFTNUM,
        t.SHIFTDATE,
        t.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
        0 as SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
        t.STATE,
        Sum(t.BINDEDSUM) as [DB_BINDEDSUM],
        Sum(COUNT) as [DB_COUNT]
    FROM
        (
        SELECT
        	tmp.RESTCODE,
	        tmp.MIDSERVER,
	        tmp.VISIT,
	        tmp.SHIFTNUM,
	        tmp.SHIFTDATE,
	        tmp.STATE,
	        ISNULL(tmp.IHIGHLEVELTYPE, 0) as IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
	        tmp.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,       
	        Round(max(tmp.BINDEDSUM), 0) as BINDEDSUM,
	        Count(tmp.BINDEDSUM)  as COUNT
	    FROM
	        (
	        SELECT
		        O.MIDSERVER, 												
		        O.VISIT, 													
		        O.ICOMMONSHIFT as SHIFTNUM,				
		        GS.SHIFTDATE, 	
		        GS.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,										
		        PC.STATE,											
		        PC.BINDEDSUM,
		        CL.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
		        R.CODE as RESTCODE
		    FROM 
		        [RK_Central].dbo.ORDERS (NOLOCK) as O
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.GLOBALSHIFTS (NOLOCK) as GS ON O.MIDSERVER = GS.MIDSERVER AND O.ICOMMONSHIFT = GS.SHIFTNUM
                     JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PRINTCHECKS (NOLOCK) as PC ON O.MIDSERVER = PC.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PC.VISIT AND O.IDENTINVISIT = PC.ORDERIDENT
                     JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.SESSIONDISHES (NOLOCK) as SD1 ON O.MIDSERVER = SD1.MIDSERVER AND O.IDENTINVISIT = SD1.ORDERIDENT AND O.VISIT = SD1.VISIT AND SD1.ISCOMBO = 0
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PAYBINDINGS (NOLOCK) as PB ON O.MIDSERVER = PB.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PB.VISIT AND PB.DISHUNI = SD1.UNI AND PB.STATE = '6'      
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.CURRLINES (NOLOCK) as CL ON O.MIDSERVER = CL.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = CL.VISIT AND PC.UNI = CL.CHECKUNI AND CL.UNI = PB.CURRUNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.TAXPARTS (NOLOCK) as TP ON O.MIDSERVER = TP.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = TP.VISIT AND PB.UNI = TP.BINDINGUNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.SESSIONDISHES (NOLOCK) as SD2 ON O.MIDSERVER = SD2.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = SD2.VISIT AND O.IDENTINVISIT = SD2.ORDERIDENT AND SD1.COMBODISHUNI = SD2.UNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PAYMENTSEXTRA (NOLOCK) as PE ON O.MIDSERVER = PE.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PE.VISIT AND CL.PAYUNIFOROWNERINFO = PE.PAYUNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.RESTAURANTS (NOLOCK) as R ON GS.IRESTAURANT = R.SIFR
                     LEFT JOIN 
                     (SELECT
                          MIDSERVER,
                          VISIT,
                          DISHUNI,
                          SUM(PRLISTSUM) 	as PRLISTSUM,
                          SUM(QUANTITY) 	as QUANTITY
                     FROM
                          [RK_Central].dbo.DISHVOIDS (NOLOCK)
                     GROUP BY
                          MIDSERVER,
                          VISIT,
                          DISHUNI) as DV ON O.MIDSERVER = DV.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = DV.VISIT AND SD1.UNI = DV.DISHUNI
		    WHERE 
		                  gs.shiftdate >= DATEADD(MONTH, DATEDIFF(MONTH, 0, getdate()), 0) and gs.shiftdate <= DATEADD(day, -6 , GETDATE())
		    )tmp 
	    Group By 
	        tmp.RESTCODE,
	        tmp.MIDSERVER,
	        tmp.VISIT,
	        tmp.SHIFTNUM,
	        tmp.SHIFTDATE,
	        ISNULL(tmp.IHIGHLEVELTYPE, 0),
            tmp.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
	        tmp.STATE
		) t
    Group By 
        t.RESTCODE,
         t.MIDSERVER,
         t.SHIFTNUM,
         t.SHIFTDATE,
         t.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
         t.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
         t.STATE

insert into rkeeper.fact_db_dt1 (RESTCODE, MIDSERVER, SHIFTNUM, SHIFTDATE, IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
        SHIFTLOADDATETIME,  STATE , DB_BINDEDSUM,   DB_COUNT)
select 
        t.RESTCODE,
        t.MIDSERVER,
        t.SHIFTNUM,
        t.SHIFTDATE,
        t.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
        0 as SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
        t.STATE,
        Sum(t.BINDEDSUM) as DB_BINDEDSUM,
        Sum(COUNT) as DB_COUNT
    FROM
        (
        SELECT
        	tmp.RESTCODE,
	        tmp.MIDSERVER,
	        tmp.VISIT,
	        tmp.SHIFTNUM,
	        tmp.SHIFTDATE,
	        tmp.STATE,
	        case when tmp.IHIGHLEVELTYPE is null then 0 else tmp.IHIGHLEVELTYPE end as IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
	        tmp.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,       
	        Round(max(tmp.BINDEDSUM), 0) as BINDEDSUM,
	        Count(tmp.BINDEDSUM)  as COUNT
	    FROM
	        (
	        SELECT
		        df.MIDSERVER, 												
		        df.VISIT, 													
		        df.SHIFTNUM,				
		        df.SHIFTDATE, 	
		        df.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,										
		        df.STATE,											
		        df.BINDEDSUM,
		        df.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
		        df.RESTCODE
		    FROM 
		        rkeeper.dt1_fact df
		    WHERE 
		        df.shiftdate >= date_trunc('month', now()) and df.shiftdate <= now() - 6*interval '1 day' 
		    )tmp
	    Group By 
	        tmp.RESTCODE,
	        tmp.MIDSERVER,
	        tmp.VISIT,
	        tmp.SHIFTNUM,
	        tmp.SHIFTDATE,
	        tmp.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
	        tmp.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
	        tmp.STATE
		) t
    Group By 
        t.RESTCODE,
         t.MIDSERVER,
         t.SHIFTNUM,
         t.SHIFTDATE,
         t.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
         t.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
         t.STATE

SELECT 
        MIDSERVER,                                                                                                  
        SHIFTNUM, 
        SHIFTLOADDATETIME,               
        SHIFTDATE  
    FROM
         RK_Central.dbo.GLOBALSHIFTS (NOLOCK) 
    WHERE 
     shiftdate >= DATEADD(MONTH, DATEDIFF(MONTH, 0, getdate()), 0)
     AND
     shiftdate <= DATEADD(day, -6 , GETDATE())

Изначально данные будут разделены на части, 
чтобы их было легче прогружать. После уже данные
отправляются на процессор загрузки в Greenplum.

В случае ошибки ( внутренняя ошибка NIFI, 
зависли данные, долгое ожидание и пр) данные еще 
несколько раз будут пробовать попасть внутрь БД 
( после нескольких попыток упадут в лог ошибок, 
если не смогли загрузиться).

Если произошла неудача при вставке данных или их обработке, 
то делается несколько попыток еще раз реализовать процесс...




Если все же не удается положить данные, то дальше идет 
запись в лог и отправке уведомления об ошибке.

Блок удаления старых данных в Greenplum

и после извлечения данных из MSSQL

Блок уведомления об ошибках

В этот блок стекаются все ошибки, которые могут произойти в ETL
процессе. Они проходят через процессор логирования информации,
записи необходимых параметров информации об ошибке и отправке на почту.

Рекомендуется раз в две недели/месяц проверять работоспособность
уведомлений на всей схеме, т.к. уведомление об ошибках на самом процессоре
отправки сообщений об ошибках не имеется.

select t2.SHIFTDATE, 
                t2.MIDSERVER, 
				t2.VISIT, 
				t2.SHIFTNUM, 
				t2.SERVICESTART, 
				t2.SERVICEEND, 
				t.OPERATION , 
				t.SERVICEPAY, 
				t.MANAGER, Getdate() as gp_load_date
from   
(SELECT distinct 
            GS.SHIFTDATE       as SHIFTDATE, 
            O.MIDSERVER        as MIDSERVER,                          
            O.VISIT            as VISIT,                            
            O.ICOMMONSHIFT      AS SHIFTNUM, 
            O.STARTSERVICE      AS SERVICESTART, 
            O.ENDSERVICE        AS SERVICEEND, 
            L.OPERATION         as OPERATION, 
            FIRST_VALUE(L.DATETIME) OVER (Partition BY L.OPERATION, L.VISIT, L.ICOMMONSHIFT, L.MIDSERVER ORDER BY L.DATETIME)   AS SERVICEPAY, 
            FIRST_VALUE(L.MANAGER) OVER (Partition BY L.OPERATION, L.VISIT, L.ICOMMONSHIFT, L.MIDSERVER ORDER BY L.DATETIME)   AS MANAGER 
        FROM  
            [RK_Central].dbo.ORDERS as O (nolock) 
            LEFT JOIN GLOBALSHIFTS as GS (nolock) ON O.MIDSERVER = GS.MIDSERVER AND O.ICOMMONSHIFT = GS.SHIFTNUM 
            LEFT JOIN OPERATIONLOG as L (nolock) ON (L.MIDSERVER = O.MIDSERVER AND L.ICOMMONSHIFT = O.ICOMMONSHIFT AND L.VISIT = O.VISIT) AND L.OPERATION in ('420', '1015', '466', '1017') 
			where gs.SHIFTDATE >= dateadd(day,-4, getdate())
                AND gs.SHIFTDATE <  getdate()

) t
right join  (SELECT distinct 
              GS.SHIFTDATE       as SHIFTDATE, 
              O.MIDSERVER        as MIDSERVER,                          
              O.VISIT            as VISIT,         
              O.ICOMMONSHIFT     AS SHIFTNUM, 
              O.STARTSERVICE      AS SERVICESTART, 
              O.ENDSERVICE        AS SERVICEEND, 
              pc2.DELETEDATETIME  AS SERVICEPAY, 
              pc2.IDELETEMANAGER  AS MANAGER 
          FROM  
              [RK_Central].dbo.ORDERS as O 
              LEFT JOIN GLOBALSHIFTS as GS (nolock) ON O.MIDSERVER = GS.MIDSERVER AND O.ICOMMONSHIFT = GS.SHIFTNUM 
          outer apply ( 
          select pc.DELETEDATETIME, pc.MIDSERVER, pc.VISIT, pc.IDELETEMANAGER, pc.STATE from PRINTCHECKS pc where pc.MIDSERVER=o.MIDSERVER and pc.VISIT=o.VISIT and pc.STATE=7) pc2 
		  where gs.SHIFTDATE >= dateadd(day,-4, getdate())
                AND gs.SHIFTDATE <  getdate()
) t2
 on t.SHIFTDATE = t2.SHIFTDATE
             and t.MIDSERVER = t2.MIDSERVER                     
             and t.VISIT = t2.VISIT  
             and t.SHIFTNUM = t2.SHIFTNUM
             and t.SERVICESTART = t2.SERVICESTART
             and t.SERVICEEND = t2.SERVICEEND
             --and t.SERVICEPAY = t2.SERVICEPAY
             --and t.MANAGER = t2.MANAGER

properties.SQL select query:
delete
from rkeeper.dt1_modifiers
where shiftdate >= now() - 4*interval'1day'

SELECT 							
        GS.SHIFTDATE,
        O.ICOMMONSHIFT as SHIFTNUM,
        DM.[VISIT],
        DM.[MIDSERVER],
        PB.[UNI],
        DM.DISHUNI,
        DM.SIFR 	as MODIFCODE,	
        cast(DM.MODICNT * PB.QUANTITY as bigint)  as MODIFIERSCOUNT,
        CL.SIFR		as MODIFIERSCURRENCY,
        cast(Round(DM.PRICE * DM.MODICNT * PB.QUANTITY,2) as bigint)	as MODIFIERSPRICE,
        CASE WHEN isnull(PB.PRICESUM,0) = 0 THEN 0
            ELSE Round(Round(DM.PRICE - DM.PRICE * isnull(DP.DP_sum,0) / PB.PRICESUM,2) * DM.MODICNT * PB.QUANTITY,2) END	as MODIFIERSSUM,
        getdate() as gp_load_date,
        GS.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
        R.CODE,
        TP.TAXRATE,
        SD.SIFR as DISHSIFR,
        O.COT AS OUTTYPE,
        (CASE WHEN PB.STATE = 6 THEN DM.MODICNT ELSE 0 END) * PB.QUANTITY AS MODIFIERSCOUNTDAX
FROM GLOBALSHIFTS (NOLOCK) as GS
LEFT JOIN RESTAURANTS (NOLOCK) R ON R.SIFR = GS.IRESTAURANT
LEFT JOIN ORDERS (NOLOCK) O ON GS.MIDSERVER = O.MIDSERVER AND GS.SHIFTNUM = O.ICOMMONSHIFT
RIGHT JOIN DISHMODIFIERS (NOLOCK) as DM ON O.VISIT = DM.VISIT AND O.MIDSERVER = DM.MIDSERVER AND O.IDENTINVISIT = DM.ORDERIDENT
     JOIN PAYBINDINGS (NOLOCK) as PB ON DM.MIDSERVER = PB.MIDSERVER AND DM.VISIT = PB.VISIT AND DM.DISHUNI = PB.DISHUNI
LEFT JOIN SESSIONDISHES SD ON PB.MIDSERVER = SD.MIDSERVER AND PB.VISIT = SD.VISIT AND PB.DISHUNI = SD.UNI
LEFT JOIN SESSIONDISHES SD2 ON SD2.MIDSERVER = SD.MIDSERVER AND SD2.VISIT = SD.VISIT AND SD2.UNI = SD.COMBODISHUNI
LEFT JOIN TAXPARTS TP ON TP.VISIT = PB.VISIT AND TP.MIDSERVER = PB.MIDSERVER AND TP.BINDINGUNI = PB.UNI AND TP.SIFR = 1
LEFT JOIN CURRLINES (NOLOCK) as CL ON CL.MIDSERVER = PB.MIDSERVER AND CL.VISIT = PB.VISIT AND CL.UNI = PB.CURRUNI
outer apply (select abs(sum(dp.sum)) as DP_sum from DISCPARTS (NOLOCK) DP where DP.MIDSERVER = PB.MIDSERVER AND DP.VISIT = PB.VISIT AND DP.BINDINGUNI = PB.UNI) DP
WHERE gs.SHIFTDATE >= dateadd(day,-4, getdate()) and gs.SHIFTDATE <= getdate()
        AND
        DM.COMBODISHUNI = 0;
vacuum(analyze) rkeeper.dt1_modifiers;

то делается несколько попыток еще раз реализовать процесс...

запись в лог и отправке уведомления об ошибке.

Блок уведомления об ошибках

В этот блок стекаются все ошибки, которые могут произойти в ETL
процессе. Они проходят через процессор логирования информации,
записи необходимых параметров информации об ошибке и отправке на почту.

Рекомендуется раз в две недели/месяц проверять работоспособность
уведомлений на всей схеме, т.к. уведомление об ошибках на самом процессоре
отправки сообщений об ошибках не имеется.

SELECT

        O1.GUIDSTRING 			    as GUID_ORDERS,

        RD1.VISIT_PC                as CHECK_VISIT,
        RD1.MIDSERVER_PC            as CHECK_MIDSERVER,
        RD1.ORDERIDENT_PC           as CHECK_ORDERIDENT,
        RD1.RETURNCHECKDATETIME_RD  as CHECK_DATE,
        RD1.GUID_ORDERS_PC          as CHECK_GUID_ORDERS,
        RD1.SHIFTNUM_PC             as CHECK_SHIFTNUM,
Getdate() as gp_load_date
    FROM 
    	[RK_Central].dbo.ORDERS as O1
 		JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PRINTCHECKS as PC1 ON O1.MIDSERVER = PC1.MIDSERVER AND O1.VISIT = PC1.VISIT AND O1.IDENTINVISIT = PC1.ORDERIDENT
        JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.SESSIONDISHES (NOLOCK) as SD1 ON O1.MIDSERVER = SD1.MIDSERVER AND O1.IDENTINVISIT = SD1.ORDERIDENT AND O1.VISIT = SD1.VISIT AND SD1.ISCOMBO = 0
        LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PAYBINDINGS (NOLOCK) as PB ON O1.MIDSERVER = PB.MIDSERVER AND O1.VISIT = PB.VISIT AND PB.DISHUNI = SD1.UNI AND PB.STATE = '6'      
        LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.CURRLINES (NOLOCK) as CL ON O1.MIDSERVER = CL.MIDSERVER AND O1.VISIT = CL.VISIT AND PC1.UNI = CL.CHECKUNI AND CL.UNI = PB.CURRUNI
        JOIN (SELECT 
				RD.VISIT 					as VISIT_RD,
				RD.MIDSERVER 				as MIDSERVER_RD,
				RD.ORDERIDENT 				as ORDERIDENT_RD,
				RD.RETURNCHECKDATETIME 		as RETURNCHECKDATETIME_RD,

				PC.VISIT 					as VISIT_PC,
				PC.MIDSERVER 				as MIDSERVER_PC,
				PC.ORDERIDENT 				as ORDERIDENT_PC,
				O.GUIDSTRING 				as GUID_ORDERS_PC,
                O.ICOMMONSHIFT 				as SHIFTNUM_PC

			FROM
			   [RK_Central].dbo.ORDERS as O
			    JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PRINTCHECKS as PC ON O.MIDSERVER = PC.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PC.VISIT AND O.IDENTINVISIT = PC.ORDERIDENT
			    JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.RETURNDATA as RD ON PC.UNI = RD.RETURNCHECKUNI  
                                                    AND PC.VISIT = RD.RETURNVISIT 
                                                    AND PC.MIDSERVER = RD.RETURNMIDSERVER 
                                                    AND PC.ORDERIDENT = RD.RETURNORDERIDENT
            WHERE 
                RD.RETURNCHECKDATETIME  = cast('${shiftdate}' as datetime) 
                AND O.ICOMMONSHIFT = cast('${shiftnum}' as int)
                AND RD.MIDSERVER = cast('${midserver}' as int)
            ) as RD1 ON RD1.VISIT_RD = PC1.VISIT 
                    AND RD1.MIDSERVER_RD = PC1.MIDSERVER 
                    AND RD1.ORDERIDENT_RD = PC1.ORDERIDENT

SELECT
        O.MIDSERVER,
        O.VISIT,
		GS.SHIFTDATE,
        O.ICOMMONSHIFT as SHIFTNUM,
Getdate() as gp_load_date
    FROM 
        [RK_Central].dbo.PRINTCHECKS (NOLOCK) PC
        LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.GENERATEDPROPDATAS (NOLOCK) GPD ON GPD.OBJECTREFNO = 71 AND GPD.RKTYPEIDENT = 1000015 AND GPD.OBJECTIDENT = PC.ICLOSESTATION
        JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.ORDERS (NOLOCK) O ON (O.VISIT = PC.VISIT) AND (O.MIDSERVER = PC.MIDSERVER) AND (O.IDENTINVISIT = PC.ORDERIDENT)
        LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.EXTERNALIDS (NOLOCK) EI ON EI.VISIT = O.VISIT AND EI.MIDSERVER = O.MIDSERVER AND EI."ORDER" = O.IDENTINVISIT
        JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.GLOBALSHIFTS (NOLOCK) GS ON (GS.MIDSERVER = O.MIDSERVER) AND (GS.SHIFTNUM = O.ICOMMONSHIFT)
        LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.RESTAURANTS (NOLOCK) R ON GS.IRESTAURANT=R.SIFR
        LEFT JOIN ( 
            SELECT 
                VISIT, 
                MIDSERVER, 
                ORDERIDENT,
                MAX(CASE WHEN ISESSIONTYPE=5 THEN 5 ELSE 0 END) AS "ISESSIONTYPE" 
            FROM 
                [RK_Central].dbo.ORDERSESSIONS (NOLOCK)
            GROUP BY
                VISIT, 
                MIDSERVER, 
                ORDERIDENT) OS
        ON (OS.MIDSERVER=O.MIDSERVER) AND (OS.VISIT=O.VISIT) AND (OS.ORDERIDENT=O.IDENTINVISIT)
    WHERE 
        OS.ISESSIONTYPE=5
        AND 
        (PC.IGNOREINREP=0)
        AND 
        (GS.STATUS=3) 
        AND 
        (EI.VISIT IS NULL OR EI.EXTSOURCE <> '120')
        AND 
        (GPD.SIFR IS NULL OR GPD.PROPERTYVAL <> '3')
        AND
        gs.shiftdate = cast('${shiftdate}' as datetime) and cast(o.midserver as int)= cast('${midserver}' as int) and cast(o.icommonshift as int) = cast('${shiftnum}' as int)

insert into rkeeper.fact_db_dt1 (RESTCODE, MIDSERVER, SHIFTNUM, SHIFTDATE, IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
        SHIFTLOADDATETIME,  STATE , DB_BINDEDSUM,   DB_COUNT)
select 
        t.RESTCODE,
        t.MIDSERVER,
        t.SHIFTNUM,
        t.SHIFTDATE,
        t.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
        0 as SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
        t.STATE,
        Sum(t.BINDEDSUM) as DB_BINDEDSUM,
        Sum(COUNT) as DB_COUNT
    FROM
        (
        SELECT
        	tmp.RESTCODE,
	        tmp.MIDSERVER,
	        tmp.VISIT,
	        tmp.SHIFTNUM,
	        tmp.SHIFTDATE,
	        tmp.STATE,
	        case when tmp.IHIGHLEVELTYPE is null then 0 else tmp.IHIGHLEVELTYPE end as IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
	        tmp.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,       
	        Round(max(tmp.BINDEDSUM), 0) as BINDEDSUM,
	        Count(tmp.BINDEDSUM)  as COUNT
	    FROM
	        (
	        SELECT
		        df.MIDSERVER, 												
		        df.VISIT, 													
		        df.SHIFTNUM,				
		        df.SHIFTDATE, 	
		        df.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,										
		        df.STATE,											
		        df.BINDEDSUM,
		        df.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
		        df.RESTCODE
		    FROM 
		        rkeeper.dt1_fact df
		    WHERE 
		        df.shiftdate >= now() - 4*interval'1 day' and df.shiftdate <= now() 
		    )tmp
	    Group By 
	        tmp.RESTCODE,
	        tmp.MIDSERVER,
	        tmp.VISIT,
	        tmp.SHIFTNUM,
	        tmp.SHIFTDATE,
	        tmp.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
	        tmp.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
	        tmp.STATE
		) t
    Group By 
        t.RESTCODE,
         t.MIDSERVER,
         t.SHIFTNUM,
         t.SHIFTDATE,
         t.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
         t.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
         t.STATE

select distinct fdd.RESTCODE as dt1_RESTCODE,
       fs2.RESTCODE as source_RESTCODE,
        fdd.MIDSERVER as dt1_MIDSERVER,
        fs2.MIDSERVER as source_MIDSERVER,
        fdd.SHIFTNUM as dt1_SHIFTNUM,
        fs2.SHIFTNUM as source_SHIFTNUM,
        fdd.SHIFTDATE as dt1_SHIFTDATE,
        fs2.SHIFTDATE as source_SHIFTDATE,
        fdd.IHIGHLEVELTYPE as dt1_IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
        fs2.IHIGHLEVELTYPE as source_IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
        fdd.SHIFTLOADDATETIME as dt1_SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
        fs2.SHIFTLOADDATETIME as source_SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
        fdd.STATE as dt1_STATE,
        fs2.STATE as source_STATE,
        fdd.DB_BINDEDSUM as dt1_DB_BINDEDSUM,
        fdd.DB_COUNT as dt1_DB_COUNT,
        fs2.DB_BINDEDSUM as source_DB_BINDEDSUM,
        fs2.DB_COUNT as source_DB_COUNT
from rkeeper.fact_source fs2  
full outer join rkeeper.fact_db_dt1 fdd on 
        fdd.RESTCODE = fs2.RESTCODE
        and 
        fdd.MIDSERVER = fs2.MIDSERVER
        and fdd.SHIFTNUM = fs2.SHIFTNUM
        and fdd.SHIFTDATE = fs2.SHIFTDATE
        and fdd.IHIGHLEVELTYPE = fs2.IHIGHLEVELTYPE
        and fdd.SHIFTLOADDATETIME = fs2.SHIFTLOADDATETIME
        and fdd.STATE = fs2.STATE 
where (fdd.DB_BINDEDSUM <> fs2.DB_BINDEDSUM or fdd.DB_COUNT <> fs2.DB_COUNT)  
or (fs2.SHIFTNUM is null)

SELECT
        t.RESTCODE,
        t.MIDSERVER,
        t.SHIFTNUM,
        t.SHIFTDATE,
        t.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
        0 as SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
        t.STATE,
        Sum(t.BINDEDSUM) as [DB_BINDEDSUM],
        Sum(COUNT) as [DB_COUNT]
    FROM
        (
        SELECT
        	tmp.RESTCODE,
	        tmp.MIDSERVER,
	        tmp.VISIT,
	        tmp.SHIFTNUM,
	        tmp.SHIFTDATE,
	        tmp.STATE,
	        ISNULL(tmp.IHIGHLEVELTYPE, 0) as IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
	        tmp.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,       
	        Round(max(tmp.BINDEDSUM), 0) as BINDEDSUM,
	        Count(tmp.BINDEDSUM)  as COUNT
	    FROM
	        (
	        SELECT
		        O.MIDSERVER, 												
		        O.VISIT, 													
		        O.ICOMMONSHIFT as SHIFTNUM,				
		        GS.SHIFTDATE, 	
		        GS.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,										
		        PC.STATE,											
		        PC.BINDEDSUM,
		        CL.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
		        R.CODE as RESTCODE
		    FROM 
		        [RK_Central].dbo.ORDERS (NOLOCK) as O
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.GLOBALSHIFTS (NOLOCK) as GS ON O.MIDSERVER = GS.MIDSERVER AND O.ICOMMONSHIFT = GS.SHIFTNUM
                     JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PRINTCHECKS (NOLOCK) as PC ON O.MIDSERVER = PC.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PC.VISIT AND O.IDENTINVISIT = PC.ORDERIDENT
                     JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.SESSIONDISHES (NOLOCK) as SD1 ON O.MIDSERVER = SD1.MIDSERVER AND O.IDENTINVISIT = SD1.ORDERIDENT AND O.VISIT = SD1.VISIT AND SD1.ISCOMBO = 0
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PAYBINDINGS (NOLOCK) as PB ON O.MIDSERVER = PB.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PB.VISIT AND PB.DISHUNI = SD1.UNI AND PB.STATE = '6'      
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.CURRLINES (NOLOCK) as CL ON O.MIDSERVER = CL.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = CL.VISIT AND PC.UNI = CL.CHECKUNI AND CL.UNI = PB.CURRUNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.TAXPARTS (NOLOCK) as TP ON O.MIDSERVER = TP.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = TP.VISIT AND PB.UNI = TP.BINDINGUNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.SESSIONDISHES (NOLOCK) as SD2 ON O.MIDSERVER = SD2.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = SD2.VISIT AND O.IDENTINVISIT = SD2.ORDERIDENT AND SD1.COMBODISHUNI = SD2.UNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PAYMENTSEXTRA (NOLOCK) as PE ON O.MIDSERVER = PE.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PE.VISIT AND CL.PAYUNIFOROWNERINFO = PE.PAYUNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.RESTAURANTS (NOLOCK) as R ON GS.IRESTAURANT = R.SIFR
                     LEFT JOIN 
                     (SELECT
                          MIDSERVER,
                          VISIT,
                          DISHUNI,
                          SUM(PRLISTSUM) 	as PRLISTSUM,
                          SUM(QUANTITY) 	as QUANTITY
                     FROM
                          [RK_Central].dbo.DISHVOIDS (NOLOCK)
                     GROUP BY
                          MIDSERVER,
                          VISIT,
                          DISHUNI) as DV ON O.MIDSERVER = DV.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = DV.VISIT AND SD1.UNI = DV.DISHUNI
		    WHERE 
		                  gs.shiftdate >= dateadd(day,-4, getdate()) and gs.shiftdate <= getdate()
		    )tmp 
	    Group By 
	        tmp.RESTCODE,
	        tmp.MIDSERVER,
	        tmp.VISIT,
	        tmp.SHIFTNUM,
	        tmp.SHIFTDATE,
	        ISNULL(tmp.IHIGHLEVELTYPE, 0),
            tmp.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
	        tmp.STATE
		) t
    Group By 
        t.RESTCODE,
         t.MIDSERVER,
         t.SHIFTNUM,
         t.SHIFTDATE,
         t.IHIGHLEVELTYPE,
         t.SHIFTLOADDATETIME,
         t.STATE

SELECT        
        GS.SHIFTDATE,
        O.ICOMMONSHIFT as SHIFTNUM,
        DM.[VISIT],
        DM.[MIDSERVER],
        PB.[UNI],
        DM.SIFR  as MODIFCODE, 
        DM.MODICNT * PB.QUANTITY  as MODIFIERSCOUNT,
        CL.SIFR  as MODIFIERSCURRENCY,
        CASE WHEN isnull(PB.PRICESUM,0) = 0 THEN 0
            ELSE Round(Round(DM.PRICE - DM.PRICE * isnull(DP.DP_sum,0) / PB.PRICESUM,2) * DM.MODICNT * PB.QUANTITY,2) END as MODIFIERSSUM,
        getdate() as gp_load_date,
        R.CODE,
        TP.TAXRATE,
        SD.SIFR as DISHSIFR,
        O.COT AS OUTTYPE,
        (CASE WHEN PB.STATE = 6 THEN DM.MODICNT ELSE 0 END) * PB.QUANTITY AS MODIFIERSCOUNTDAX
FROM GLOBALSHIFTS (NOLOCK) as GS
LEFT JOIN RESTAURANTS (NOLOCK) R ON R.SIFR = GS.IRESTAURANT
LEFT JOIN ORDERS (NOLOCK) O ON GS.MIDSERVER = O.MIDSERVER AND GS.SHIFTNUM = O.ICOMMONSHIFT
RIGHT JOIN DISHMODIFIERS (NOLOCK) as DM ON O.VISIT = DM.VISIT AND O.MIDSERVER = DM.MIDSERVER AND O.IDENTINVISIT = DM.ORDERIDENT
     JOIN PAYBINDINGS (NOLOCK) as PB ON DM.MIDSERVER = PB.MIDSERVER AND DM.VISIT = PB.VISIT AND DM.DISHUNI = PB.DISHUNI
LEFT JOIN SESSIONDISHES SD ON PB.MIDSERVER = SD.MIDSERVER AND PB.VISIT = SD.VISIT AND PB.DISHUNI = SD.UNI
LEFT JOIN SESSIONDISHES SD2 ON SD2.MIDSERVER = SD.MIDSERVER AND SD2.VISIT = SD.VISIT AND SD2.UNI = SD.COMBODISHUNI
LEFT JOIN TAXPARTS TP ON TP.VISIT = PB.VISIT AND TP.MIDSERVER = PB.MIDSERVER AND TP.BINDINGUNI = PB.UNI AND TP.SIFR = 1
LEFT JOIN CURRLINES (NOLOCK) as CL ON CL.MIDSERVER = PB.MIDSERVER AND CL.VISIT = PB.VISIT AND CL.UNI = PB.CURRUNI
outer apply (select abs(sum(dp.sum)) as DP_sum from DISCPARTS (NOLOCK) DP where DP.MIDSERVER = PB.MIDSERVER AND DP.VISIT = PB.VISIT AND DP.BINDINGUNI = PB.UNI) DP
WHERE gs.shiftdate = cast('${shiftdate}' as datetime) and o.midserver = cast('${midserver}' as int) and o.icommonshift = cast('${shiftnum}' as int)
        AND
        DM.COMBODISHUNI = 0;

                     JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PRINTCHECKS (NOLOCK) as PC ON O.MIDSERVER = PC.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PC.VISIT AND O.IDENTINVISIT = PC.ORDERIDENT
                     JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.SESSIONDISHES (NOLOCK) as SD1 ON O.MIDSERVER = SD1.MIDSERVER AND O.IDENTINVISIT = SD1.ORDERIDENT AND O.VISIT = SD1.VISIT AND SD1.ISCOMBO = 0
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PAYBINDINGS (NOLOCK) as PB ON O.MIDSERVER = PB.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PB.VISIT AND PB.DISHUNI = SD1.UNI AND PB.STATE = '6'      
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.CURRLINES (NOLOCK) as CL ON O.MIDSERVER = CL.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = CL.VISIT AND PC.UNI = CL.CHECKUNI AND CL.UNI = PB.CURRUNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.TAXPARTS (NOLOCK) as TP ON O.MIDSERVER = TP.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = TP.VISIT AND PB.UNI = TP.BINDINGUNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.SESSIONDISHES (NOLOCK) as SD2 ON O.MIDSERVER = SD2.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = SD2.VISIT AND O.IDENTINVISIT = SD2.ORDERIDENT AND SD1.COMBODISHUNI = SD2.UNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.PAYMENTSEXTRA (NOLOCK) as PE ON O.MIDSERVER = PE.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = PE.VISIT AND CL.PAYUNIFOROWNERINFO = PE.PAYUNI
                     LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.RESTAURANTS (NOLOCK) as R ON GS.IRESTAURANT = R.SIFR
                     LEFT JOIN 
                     (SELECT
                          MIDSERVER,
                          VISIT,
                          DISHUNI,
                          SUM(PRLISTSUM) 	as PRLISTSUM,
                          SUM(QUANTITY) 	as QUANTITY
                     FROM
                          [RK_Central].dbo.DISHVOIDS (NOLOCK)
                     GROUP BY
                          MIDSERVER,
                          VISIT,
                          DISHUNI) as DV ON O.MIDSERVER = DV.MIDSERVER AND O.VISIT = DV.VISIT AND SD1.UNI = DV.DISHUNI
                     --LEFT JOIN [RK_Central].dbo.ZREPORTDATA (NOLOCK) as ZR ON O.MIDSERVER = ZR.MIDSERVER AND O.ICOMMONSHIFT = ZR.SHIFTNUM
                 WHERE
                    gs.shiftdate = cast('${shiftdate}' as datetime) 
                    and cast(o.midserver as int)= cast('${midserver}' as int)
